"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:53:38.000Z","msg":"慢啦<br />\n我地1月2號已啟動全民口罩，仲要慘被武漢小粉紅恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ma0Af4Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMa0Af4Z.png&h=6528c27b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:57:02.000Z","msg":"回力標+binc"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:59:12.000Z","msg":"變左屍訓低左啦<br />\n中唔到回力鏢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:06:31.000Z","msg":"但係可以bin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fcda9fdb4861725ca4baf98021b4f0e2ab8a4cc","tid":1884292,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23e96a24e942b5aaf190c77af39d9d6fa6f32fe0","tid":1884292,"uid":50745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3d1f8f9546c8bd493e9941b40374282001672b2e","tid":1884292,"uid":226956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8a8b10958bba35e46dd5b229d548099c62fa72c","tid":1884292,"uid":36901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:53:38.000Z","msg":"慢啦<br />\n我地1月2號已啟動全民口罩，仲要慘被武漢小粉紅恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ma0Af4Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMa0Af4Z.png&h=6528c27b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:57:02.000Z","msg":"回力標+binc"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:59:12.000Z","msg":"變左屍訓低左啦<br />\n中唔到回力鏢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:07:59.000Z","msg":"So sad, 好多武漢人已經冚家富貴左。"},{"pid":"3715add7ea248fc137d1279ca6e092a0cf983c1b","tid":1884292,"uid":276989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:08:46.000Z","msg":"呢個好似係程序既一部份，武漢市長12月底之前已經上報實驗室份report，呢個屬於sars之後訂立既通報機制，只係習近平最後選擇唔同支那人講，但係內部機制有正常運行，所以軍隊同核心部門會有內類通告<br />\n<br />\n共產黨內部文件係會做足，會用來問罪既<br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩up"},{"pid":"f7f0a5b95bd3972347377905070be473f235b5ca","tid":1884292,"uid":16137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:14:04.000Z","msg":"香港政府 2019年12月31日已經知<br />\n中共內部又點會唔知<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201912/31/P2019123100860.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201912%2F31%2FP2019123100860.htm&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=cb571889\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201912/31/P2019123100860.htm</a>"},{"pid":"15b35ec32529889b155a68044ca6169df647b51e","tid":1884292,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:54:10.000Z","msg":"議員日日鬧爆支共無人理<br />\n跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=c30e8895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"ac122481b0792e5fd7cc12a44be861d1466c8d0c","tid":1884292,"uid":52056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T17:23:16.000Z","msg":"支共內部都叫隻病毒 Wuhan-Hu-1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}